ggrab---------------------------------------------

03.11.2002	Version	0.01	First try 
03.11.2002	Version 0.02	Fixed integer overflow at 2 G
04.11.2002	Version 0.03	Fixed some compiler errors with g++ 2.95, 
				fixed coredump at start with wrong
				dbox address, added cygwin support (not tested), 
				added large file support
04.11.2002	Version 0.04	Fixed Segmentation fault
04.11.2002	Version 0.05	Adaptions for cygwin, only signal handling doesnt work
08.11.2002	Version 0.06	adapted to Mac OS X, cancel program with q<cr> now possible
09.11.2002	Version 0.07  	Audio Part rewritten. Some more FTAs are working now
				Added Options vlog und alog für logging stream directly
10.11.2002	Version 0.08	Correction Audiostream (slow playback, streamingserver added, 
				stopping of sectionsd during recording
17.11.2002	Version 0.09	Mpeg stream improved (no warning in xine any more).
				Several other improvements. 
17.11.2002	Version 0.09a	Bug mit kaputten Bildern beseitigt, sserver jetzt im Pfad startbar
07.12.2002	Version 0.10	Verschiedene Korrekturen, Experiment udp support
